# NOLidarWireframeContour — Project Memory

## Active focus

ACT Phase 2 standalone: Lidar Wireframe Contour (NOLoader mod).

## Architecture

- **Probe:** `LidarSphereCastProbe` — Cast#1/Cast#2 origin offset; `TerrainLayerMask=2112`; min hit 12m
- **Tick:** `INOModTickNormal` — `FadeTick(dt)` + `ProbeTick` 0.2s (no MonoBehaviour Update)
- **GPU:** `LidarDepthCapturePass` (AfterRenderingTransparents) + `LidarWireframeRenderPass` (backbuffer FullScreenPass on Main Camera)
- **Uniforms:** probe/blend on CPU; `_InvViewProjMatrix` only in pass `Execute`
- **VRAM:** `LidarWireframeRenderPass.Cleanup()` → RTHandle.Release on Shutdown / blend=0 / controller OnDestroy
- **Depth:** `requiresDepthTexture` while blend>0 OR `ForceKeepDepthTextureActive`
- **Patches:** `FlightHud::Awake`, `FlightHud::SetAircraft` + `EnsureController()` fallback

## Deploy

`.\scripts\deploy-mod.ps1` → `Nuclear Option\NOLoader\mods\LidarWireframeContour\`

## Version

0.1.0 Build DEV1P37VA

## Project specifics

- Runtime requires `NOLoader.LidarWireframeContour.dll` + `NOLidarWireframeContour_Data/lidar_shaders` (loose Shaders/ NOT used; hash in `shader_source_hash.txt`)
- build-shader-bundle.ps1 syncs Data/Shaders → UnityBundleBuilder before Unity build
- Composite: backbuffer fullscreen (FullScreenPass pattern), not swap-blip only
- Edge: Laplacian + NMS + `EdgeTexelScale` (P37 thin lines)
- Mode 0 combat: impact band + smooth cone (`ConeFalloffCos`) + CRT scanlines/noise + `DistanceFadeMeters`
- Mode 3 = terrain edge debug without HUD effects

